  WCM only makes 1 style felt and that is what you got, no notchs, cuts etc,
just a cheap blow felted extrusion.. That is why I sell parts from numerous
different suppliers to get the BEST of what is out there. Wolfsburg West are
made in Brazil. I have Italian (had those made) and Brazil.

ronnie

ps. Just made; window slider base felts for the windows without the holes.
These are available for trade only,limited sets. The manufacturer is always
looking for cool bus parts (not cheap)

